      "file_path": "dmaap-sim/src/main/java/org/onap/dmaap/sim/provider/DmaapSimProvider.java",
      "patchset_number": 3,
      "line": 43,
      "message": "should be 15ms by default, but use the passed-in value otherwise.\n\nDon't bother waiting, just use a blocking queue and await(desired-timeout).",
